    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but everyone says that, and it just feels like they don't get it. they tell me \"it gets better\" or \"time heals everything\" but that feels like such a lie. i look at my life and there's nothing left. the person who made my life worth living is gone. if i'm just supposed to keep existing in this void, then what's even the point? it just feels like i'm waiting for a pain that's never gonna stop.",
